{"tid":1479741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今年夏天  一部影片道盡港人心聲 全球都聽見了.....","createTime":"2019-08-17T04:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T16:40:14.000Z","uid":184679,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1093a8156d52b9839fba8789da9d5f4f56ca8b62","tid":1479741,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T04:30:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpHeCiW3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpHeCiW3.jpg&h=5168aca9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n今年夏天的香港是什麼樣子呢？YouTube帳號「Free HongKong」昨日發布一則影片，完整記錄香港「反送中」事件經過，影片中一名男子說，「這段日子，大家都流下了很多眼淚，但今次在眼淚的背後，給了我們希望」，聲聲訴說著港人堅定「反送中」的決心與期盼。<br />\n<br />\n影片開頭寫著，「我們在此真誠致歉，我們實在感到不安、感到惶恐，警察向我們開槍，政府漠視我們的聲音，社會制度讓我們失望」，畫面中幾萬名港人彎腰鞠躬，「請支持我們」。<br />\n<br />\n影片記錄著自6月6日香港法律界發起黑衣遊行，表達對《逃犯條例》修訂的不滿，6月9日103萬名港人上街高喊「林鄭下台」，6月12日港人阻止草案二讀，警方開始對港人施放催淚彈、橡膠彈與布袋彈等武器，直至今日「反送中」示威者仍持續不斷抗爭當中。<br />\n<br />\n影片內文寫到，至今已經過2個多月，港人仍得不到政府的正面回應，而平息紛爭的方法只有林鄭月娥回應正視及實行5大訴求，徹底撤回逃犯條例、撤回612暴動定性、必不追究反送中抗爭者、成立獨立委員會，徹查警方濫權濫暴、全面落實雙真普選。<br />\n<br />\n港人短短幾日成功募資，在世界各家報紙上刊登廣告，傳達港人正歷經「反送中」抗爭的心聲，影片尾聲，全球各家報紙包含英國《衛報》（The Guardian）、《泰晤士報》（The Times）、《倫敦晚期報》（Evening Standard）、《旁觀者》（The Spectator）、《新政治家》（New Statesman）、德國《南德意志報》（S&uuml;ddeutsche Zeitung）、美國《紐約時報》（The New York Times）、《華盛頓郵報》（The Washington Post）、日本《朝日新聞》（The Asahi Shimbun）、《日本時報》（ジャパンタイムズ）、澳洲《澳洲人報》（The Australian）等共計23個國家都聽見港人的心聲，為他們加油打氣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CsjiZD2E6h0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCsjiZD2E6h0&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75VKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=2bdf43c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CsjiZD2E6h0</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2887310\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2887310&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75VKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=ea666595\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2887310&h=10f3e9b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2887310</a>"},{"pid":"cb0cc9f309561488933bfc443c5352fcb903bd0e","tid":1479741,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T04:31:15.000Z","msg":"催淚過催淚彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"310966a0ad7a302078e818243c9a10806f497ea1","tid":1479741,"uid":270220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T04:32:41.000Z","msg":"香港人好辛酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f10cec942a5c72b26e7f2026e7446d7f20545018","tid":1479741,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:41:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1bfff3d3d500c20adf967c397528b2d0eb270b8","tid":1479741,"uid":187510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:45:38.000Z","msg":"睇完記得LIKE同SUBSCRIBE埋啊 咁樣先可以俾更多人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfad3bdf8ffac359964baf30d4465b19a955e183","tid":1479741,"uid":112648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:53:49.000Z","msg":"睇到喊"},{"pid":"dec0cb65679eadcb68af791a4396aaf17aaabf9e","tid":1479741,"uid":276162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08